Package: isdbayes
Title: Fit Hierarchical Bayesian Models of Individual Size Distributions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeff", "Wesner", , "jeff.wesner@usd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6058-7972"))
Description: Adds a truncated pareto log probability density function to brms. This allows size spectra to be analyzed individually or across predictors using standard brms (or lmer) syntax.
